xation process is 35 times faster. The observed\nratio of the tunneling rates is in reasonable agreement with that calculated\nfrom the tunneling splitting, i.e. the energy difference between the two almost\ndegenerate lowest levels Ms = +/-10, in the two clusters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jan 2001 15:50:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
